scene.message:
Michiko: M-me, lose?!{nl}
That... that can't be!!{waitkey}{clearbox}And to mere humans like{nl}
these, of all things...{nl}
Ohh!? How can it be?{waitkey}Ohh!! Ooooh!!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Noisy woman.{nl}
You lost and we won -{nl}
an unbendable reality.{waitkey}{clearbox}Making your unsightly face{nl}
uglier still and raising a{nl}
fuss won't change that.{waitkey}{clearbox}A loser should act like one{nl}
and vanish from our sight{nl}
at once...{waitkey}{clearbox}No - please, vanish.{nl}
I beg you.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Ahh! Ahh!!{nl}
Aaagh!!! You're so noisy!{nl}
You are!!{waitkey}{clearbox}Listen? You got beaten by{nl}
"the dashing great me and{nl}
my pals"!!{waitkey}{clearbox}Quit squawking "ow, ow" like{nl}
a fur seal forever and get{nl}
out of my sight!{waitkey}Eh? Eh?{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Mm-hm,{nl}
exactly, like!{waitkey}{clearbox}A hopeless, super-dumb{nl}
woman's face like yours{waitkey}{clearbox}- Ayase doesn't wanna see it{nl}
anymore either, kinda?{waitkey}{clearbox}Mm... I mean, like,{nl}
just hurry up{nl}
and disappear already!{waitkey}{ret}

Michiko: Kiiiii!{nl}
Kiiiiiiiii!!{waitkey}{clearbox}What! What!! Whaaat!!!{waitkey}{clearbox}Selfish, cruel humans,{nl}
all of you?? That's what{nl}
you are!!{waitkey}{clearbox}Five of you ganging up to{nl}
bully poor me, who did{nl}
nothing, and gloating!!{waitkey}{clearbox}Yes! Humans are always like{nl}
this!! And so are you!{waitkey}{clearbox}And so are the ones whose{nl}
ugly faces hang on my wall -{waitkey}{clearbox}the ones who once bullied me{nl}
for no reason at all!{waitkey}{clearbox}Can you understand? Using my{nl}
endless money to buy the role{nl}
of "the Snow Queen"!{waitkey}{clearbox}Getting that detestable girl{nl}
playing girlfriend beside the{nl}
drama senpai I admired{nl}
expelled!{waitkey}{clearbox}Bribing a teacher to add a{nl}
little color to my grades -{nl}
that's all I did!!{waitkey}{clearbox}Yet the fools in my class{nl}
cursed frail me, gossiped{nl}
behind my back,{waitkey}{clearbox}and cast me out...{waitkey}{clearbox}The only one who gently{nl}
reached out a hand to me was{nl}
the "Snow Queen's mask"!{waitkey}{clearbox}The only one who understood{nl}
my sorrow, my misfortune, was{nl}
the "Snow Queen's mask"!{waitkey}{clearbox}Tell me, by what right do{nl}
humans bully poor,{nl}
pitiful me??{waitkey}{clearbox}Michiko... cannot understand{nl}
it at all!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: That is... entirely{nl}
your own fault!!{waitkey}{clearbox}You... you truly threw away{nl}
your life in the real world{waitkey}{clearbox}over that, sank to being the{nl}
"Snow Queen's" underling, and{nl}
became this tower's guardian?{waitkey}I'm too dumbfounded to speak.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: What? That is entirely{nl}
your own fault!!{waitkey}{clearbox}Did you really... throw away{nl}
your life in reality over{nl}
such a reason{waitkey}{clearbox}and become the "Snow Queen's"{nl}
subordinate?{waitkey}{clearbox}Unbelievable... You really{nl}
are quite unhinged...{waitkey}{ret}

Michiko: Kiiiii!!!{nl}
Even after hearing my sad{nl}
past, which I can't tell{waitkey}without tears,{waitkey}{clearbox}you can still mock me?{nl}
Michiko can't believe it!{waitkey}{clearbox}That's quite enough!! Asking{nl}
poor-hearted folk like you{waitkey}{clearbox}to grasp the sorrow of{nl}
high-society me was too much!{waitkey}{clearbox}Hmph! Fine!! Just this once,{nl}
I'll let it be your win!!{waitkey}{clearbox}But be prepared... when the{nl}
vengeance for you swirling in{nl}
my heart fills once{nl}
more in time!{waitkey}{clearbox}I shall show you hell{nl}
again!!{waitkey}{clearbox}Reeemember this!! I'll appear{nl}
before you again and again!{waitkey}{clearbox}Look forward to that day!!{nl}
Now then, good day!{waitkey}{clearbox}Ohohohoho!{nl}
Ohohohohohoho!{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Michiko Matsudaira...{nl}
someone I'd rather never{nl}
meet again.{waitkey}{clearbox}Oh, right! Toro and Kuroori...{nl}
are they okay?{waitkey}{clearbox}That Michiko! She never{nl}
handed over the key after{nl}
all!!{waitkey}{clearbox}When we get back to school,{nl}
let's go check on those two.{nl}
Now, let's head back!{waitkey}{ret}
